ash-865463533190374v", "ext": "mp4", "width": 1080, "height": 1920, "tbr": 1303.334, "format_note": "DASH video", "container": "mp4_dash", "vcodec": "vp09.00.40.08.00.01.01.01.00", "acodec": "none", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m367/AQMPnl7C6ycjEjJGTuUbPymZIeZSVLPa_dNTjjmboIYTVv7_821YBR-iKOsCopmNPYB3jHyExhKHVVH6OQudaVnHBYfYCvu14pDsCUY.mp4?_nc_cat=105&_nc_sid=9ca052&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=JMhlHc_2v_8Q7kNvwGzh3e_&&ccb=17-1&_nc_gid=3kIVrotH1m_sIx34rWW7EQ&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ss=7a32e&oh=00_Af2uQYQy3FEPmDe05Vx48i5c1kDQce-1AohMawuHvWAsxw&oe=69D4C572", "manifest_stream_number": 0, "is_dash_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 1303.334, "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 14314843, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-865463533190374v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by sheinspiration___", "description": "Most parents would NEVER knowingly give their kids something that harms them…\n\nBut what if the things we were taught are “normal”…\nare actually the problem?\n\nThe same system that normalized sugary breakfast cereals for kids\nwas built on marketing, not health.\n\nBright boxes. Cartoon characters. “Part of a balanced breakfast.”\n\nMeanwhile…\nwe’re seeing more kids struggle with energy crashes, focus issues, weight gain, and blood sugar problems earlier than ever.\n\nThis isn’t about guilt — it’s about awareness.\n\nBecause once you SEE it, you can’t unsee it.\n\nI had to unlearn a lot too.\nAnd when I did, everything changed — not just for me, but for my kids and my whole family.\n\nWe did